text: Baklushi () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bolshesosnovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 363 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 10 km west from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Baklushi
